					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can certainly DMA a whole non-scrolling tile <em>map.</em> That's only 32*28*2 = 1792 bytes. You can also DMA in new columns or rows as the scrolling window reaches them. It's just DMAing in new <em>tiles</em> that might cause delay.</div>

